    q: `A bus travels $60 \\text{ km}$ total, with the first $30 \\text{ km}$ at $30 \\text{ km/h}$. What must be the speed for the remaining $30 \\text{ km}$ if the average speed for the whole trip must be $40 \\text{ km/h}$?`,
